Name: Coffee For Robots
About the game: Make coffee for robots! Get sued! Run a small café, serving up coffee for the robotic denizens of the world. Make coffee to order, gain higher online reviews to increase traffic to your café. Shop for daily supplies. Balance cost and profit to keep your café running for one more day.
